ool-libraries-look-to-bridge-the-gap-of-reading-progress-lost-in-lockdowns"><img loading="lazy" src="https&#x3a;&#x2f;&#x2f;drsw10gc90t0z.cloudfront.net&#x2f;AcuCustom&#x2f;Sitename&#x2f;DAM&#x2f;430&#x2f;Summer_Reading_Challenge_Thumb.jpg" alt="School&#x20;libraries&#x20;look&#x20;to&#x20;bridge&#x20;the&#x20;gap&#x20;of&#x20;reading&#x20;progress&#x20;lost&#x20;in&#x20;lockdowns" title="School&#x20;libraries&#x20;look&#x20;to&#x20;bridge&#x20;the&#x20;gap&#x20;of&#x20;reading&#x20;progress&#x20;lost&#x20;in&#x20;lockdowns" class="aos-ArticleImage aos-Image aos-MW100" /></a></div><div class="aos-ArticleTextContainer aos-OFH aos-DynWidth aos-FL aos-W66 aos-PRM5"><h2 class="aos-ArticleTitle aos-DS21-H2 aos-FL100 aos-BW aos-M0 aos-DF aos-TAL"><a href="https://www.thebookseller.com/features/school-libraries-look-to-bridge-the-gap-of-reading-progress-lost-in-lockdowns" >School libraries look to bridge the gap of reading progress lost in lockdowns</a></h2></div></div></div></div></div></div></div>
